io.springlets.data.web.datatables

Class ConvertedDatatablesData<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.springlets.data.web.datatables.DatatablesData<Map<String,Object>>
      • io.springlets.data.web.datatables.ConvertedDatatablesData<T>

  • public class ConvertedDatatablesData<T>
extends DatatablesData<Map<String,Object>>
    Response data for data requests performed by datatables component. The data is converted through a ConversionService to a Map of String values with each object bean property as the key. It may also take into account the columns parameters sent by the datatables to convert only the needed properties. The current Locale is also taken into account, so this class allows to send data to a datatables using the same conversion which is used in the application pages.
    Author:
    Cèsar Ordiñana at http://www.disid.com[DISID Corporation S.L.]
